verbose_text: The effect of IJSP dose on the amount of AB25 adsorbed was obtained by adding different amounts of IJSP (10, 30, 50, 80, 100, 150, 200, and 250 mg) into a number of 50 mL Stoppered glass Erlenmeyer flasks containing a definite volume (25 mL in each case) of fixed initial concentration (50 mg L -1) of solution without changing pH (5.44) at temperature, 35 +/- 1degreesC.
